+template("Hank's Haute Dogs", "menu")
  section
    .row
      #intro.large-7.large-push-5.columns.pull-up
        p Hank's Haute Dogs is a great place to chow down on an American staple done with a twist. Pick a classic or get haute. Hank's Dogs taste great on their own, but pair them with sides like Hank's Awesome French Fries and you'll be in Haute Dog Heaven.
    #menu
      #classic.row
        .large-3.columns.category
          img(src="images/menu_classic.png")
        .large-9.columns
          ul.large-block-grid-4.small-block-grid-2.medium-block-grid-3
            li
              img(src="images/dog_chicago.png")
              p Genuine Chicago Vienna all-beef hot dog with the famous snap! Try one with everything!
            li
              img(src="images/dog_polish.png")
              p Another Chicago favorite, big bold, flavor, pile it on!
            li
              img(src="images/dog_chili.png")
              p Chicago Dog with Hank's homemade chili, raw onion and cheddar cheese.
      #haute.row
        .large-3.columns.category
          img(src="images/menu_haute.png")
        .large-9.columns
          ul.large-block-grid-4.small-block-grid-2.medium-block-grid-3
            li
              img(src="images/dog_hawaiian.png")
              p Portuguese sausage with mango mustard and pineapple relish.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_brat.png")
              p Classic steamed, Dusseldorf mustard and sauerkraut.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_chorizo.png")
              p Grilled, brown mustard, grilled onion and cilantro.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_andouille.png")
              p Grilled, spicy with onion and Cajun spiced mustard.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_chicken.png")
              p Grilled Chicken Sausage, sweet mango relish, lime mustard.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_nodog.png")
              p Avocado, tomato, onion, cucumber, Chinese parsley, spicy chipotle mayo and cheddar.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_fatboy.png")
              p Our best dog wrapped in bacon, deep fried served with mayo, tomato and lettuce...HDBLT!
      #daily.row
        .large-3.columns.category
          img(src="images/menu_daily.png")
        .large-9.columns
          ul.large-block-grid-4.small-block-grid-2.medium-block-grid-3
            li
              img(src="images/dog_italianBeef.png")
              p <strong>MONDAY</strong><br />
                | Every Monday we serve the infamous Chicago Italian Beef, Homemade Italian Sausage or both!
            li
              img(src="images/dog_wildBoar.png")
              p <strong>TUESDAY</strong><br />
                | Cran-apple relish, black pepper-thyme mustard, lettuce.
            li
              img(src="images/dog_alligator.png")
